to compile:

rm -f fill
c++ -Wall `root-config --cflags` -o fill fill.cc          \
  read.cc EventDiscriminatorFill.cc EventDiscriminator.cc \
  DiscriminatorFill.cc DiscriminatorBase.cc `root-config --libs`

rm -f disc
c++ -Wall `root-config --cflags` -o disc disc.cc          \
  read.cc EventDiscriminatorRead.cc EventDiscriminator.cc \
  DiscriminatorRead.cc DiscriminatorBase.cc DiscAnalysis.cc `root-config --libs`

or

compile

------------

to run:

fill train.txt hDist.root

disc test.txt hDist.root hDisc.root

"train.txt" and "test.txt" files can be found in the discData directory
